spec.name: kube-system/my-test-jql-search
spec.details:
The pod named "kube-scheduler" does not have any endpoints associated with it. This may be caused by the absence of a label component=kube-scheduler in the pods that the service is supposed to be routing traffic to.

To fix this issue, ensure that all pods associated with the "kube-scheduler" service have the label "component=kube-scheduler" added. This will allow the service to correctly route traffic to the pods.

error.text: Service has no endpoints, expected label component=kube-scheduler
